keyFacts: A comprehensive financial subpoena was issued targeting Ghislaine Maxwell and her associated corporate entities (Terramar Project Inc., Ellmax LLC, Max Foundation, Max Hotel Services Corp).
The subpoena demands all records from account inception, including transaction documents, signature cards, identification, wire transfers, safe deposit records, and all electronic correspondence.
The request includes detailed electronic banking data such as IP addresses, MAC addresses, and online session logs, indicating a forensic financial investigation.
The document is part of a larger case file, referenced by number EFTA00089197, with a contact at EFTA00089198.
